{'id': 3599710, 'body': "The timing was funny, but yes, it was actually a coincidence. Transit is a valued partner of ours and we look forward to a continued integration with them. Their app is indeed great-- that's a big part of the reason we're so happy with the partnership. We are constantly striving to improve our app so we value your feedback about the in-app sponsorships. Nobody likes ads, but we aim to make them unobtrusive. By your feedback, it sounds like we missed the mark a bit. Thank you again and we'll take this into consideration. 

Cheers,
Jake & The Divvy App Team", 'modified': '2018-05-25T17:43:43Z'}
